        <ArticleTitle>[Elucidation of the Role of Dorsal Raphe Serotonergic Neurons in Mood Regulation Using Pharmacological and Viral Vector-based Approaches].</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>341</StartPage>
